As soon as he came on the beach, Gesper started doing some 
stretchings. Being techno-organic, this would make his long and 
depleting swim easier. He opened his comm.

Gesper: Gesper to Shadow Destiny. I am about to swim to the base. 
Please confirm follow-up of my progression. Over.

Daemos: Follow-up confirmed. As soon as the Hellgate is modified, 
we'll come and get you. Good luck, Prophet. Shadow Destiny over and 
out.

Gesper was not pleased by this challenge, but he knew he had to do it. 
It did not worry him, though, because he was a good swimmer. In fact, 
he was able to cover great distances in calm waters, yet this ocean 
was barely calm...

He threw himself in and started swimming...
